tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Ḥā Mīm. The discussion on similar letters has already passed in Sūrah Al-Baqarah."
  43,2,"Allah takes an oath on the Qur’ān which clearly explains the path of guidance towards the truth."
  43,6,"How many a messenger did I send in previous nations."
  43,7,"Whenever a prophet came to those previous nations from Allah they used to mock at him."